This directory contains the Guile Ares RS 0.9.7 release from
https://git.sr.ht/~abcdw/guile-ares-rs, commit
661fd97d520e63f72f60bd965ce604bba7dc80cd.

Cind loads the Scheme modules under src/guile directly. Upstream sources are
distributed under GPL-3.0-or-later; see LICENSE.

The `(ares completion)`, `(ares lookup)`, and `(ares repl)` modules expose
protocol-independent development primitives. The nREPL completion and lookup
extensions adapt those primitives to their wire representations. Cind's command
loop consumes the protocol-independent modules directly.
